Package core

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    CBot
    CBot.java --- The Bot-class itself of which an instance gets created.
    ChokePointPolygonGenerator
    ChokePointPolygonGenerator.java --- Class for generating Polygons around ChokePoints.
    Core
    Core.java --- A class that holds the most important game information on which other classes rely on.
    Display
    Display.java --- A class used for displaying all sorts of basic information on the map and on the screen.
    Init
    Init.java --- Class used for the initialization of the most important instances.
    Main
    Main.java --- Main class.
    PolygonContenderFactory
    PolygonContenderFactory.java --- Class for generating Polygons which define a area in which no worker is allowed to construct buildings in.
    TilePositionContenderFactory
    TilePositionContenderGenerator.java --- Class for generating the default contended construction spots on the map, on which no worker can construct a building.
    TilePositionFactory
    FactorySuperclass.java --- Superclass for worker actions depending on knowledge of needed TilePositions.
